  "body": "### Description\r\nTransitioning to BLOCKHEADER mode uses the previous (contract-mode) block's validators but doesn't update the VoteTallyCache. This means subsequent blocks will get an old or possibly empty validator list.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* `contract -> blockheader` should not stop mining\r\n* `blockheader(vals1) -> contract (vals2) -> blockheader` should use vals2 from the transition block onwards\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Set up a network using CONTRACT mode in the genesis block\r\n2. Transition to BLOCKHEADER mode\r\n3. Transition will work and produce the next block but then it will stop mining\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:**\r\nMining continues beyond the transition block\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior:**\r\nMining stops the block after the transition\r\n\r\n",
